node.text:
@themillennialmoneymentor Your investment portfolio doesn’t have to look like the invisible boat mobile
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
I know social media is flooded with all kinds of “get rich quick” content and because of how the algorithm works, that’s the type of content that gets pushed onto your timeline
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
I have no problem with people wanting to become wealthier sooner than later, but you have to manage your expectations about the options you have available to you
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
All “roads” to building wealth have their unique pros & cons. Some are much easier than others. But usually, the easier ones also take more time.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
If your goal is to “get rich quick”, investing is probably not the right vehicle for you
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The point of investing is to build enough wealth in order to achieve future financial goals that are specific to you
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Speaking of, my brand new 5 Day investing workshop is now OPEN 📈
@themillennialmoneymentor ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Learn how to approach investing and your finances in general the right way and learn what it will to build the wealth that’s necessary to achieve your future financial goals
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Workshop goes Live on 8/23. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
To save your seat, see the link in @themillennialmoneymentor bio. 🤝

DEFI IS SHORT FOR "DECENTRALIZED FINANCE, A GENERAL TERM FOR A VARIETY OF FINANCIAL APPLICATIONS IN CRYPTOCURRENCY OR BLOCKCHAIN GEARED TOWARD DISRUPTING TRADITIONAL FINANCIAL INTERMEDIARIES. Lending Exchanges Asset Management Payments Derivatives Escrow VEROXAI'.

node.text:
Decentralized finance (commonly referred to as DeFi) is a blockchain-based form of finance that does not rely on central financial intermediaries such as brokerages, exchanges, or banks to offer traditional financial instruments, and instead utilizes smart contracts on blockchains.

Excited to be working with VeroxAi to educate everyone on the benefits of decentralized finance!

They also just released their beta app today! Check it out on the App Store!

node.text:
With @investvint investing in whiskey has never been easier!

With the rarest bottles selling for millions, single malt whiskies have long been some of the most coveted and expensive spirits on earth. This has been further born out in the Knight Frank Wealth Report, where whisky has been the leader in the passion asset category for the last 10 years. This passion has translated to the value of collectible whisky sharply rising over the last decade, growing 373% in value since 2013 according to recognized industry authority Rare Whisky 101’s Apex 100 Index. Leading this growth has been Macallan, whose whiskies account for nearly 40% of the collectible whisky market share. Over the past 12 months, Macallan whiskies have outpaced the market, increasing 22% in value compared to the RW Apex 1000, which has increased 11%.

Macallan Dominates Market Share Seeing 22% growth in value over the last 
12 months, Macallan’s whiskies makeup nearly 40% of collectible whisky value market share and are considered a necessity for any serious whisky 
investment portfolio.

Get started investing today in a unique asset with @investvint
